videos.description: Alonzo Verge Jr. drives to the basket, but Arizona's Ira Lee jumps up and blocks the shot.
videos.headline: Lee rejects Verge's layup

videos.description: Arizona State passes the ball around without it ever touching the floor, eventually landing in Remy Martin's hands who scores with 2 seconds left in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (ASU's good ball movement leads to Martin's layup) 2020/01/25
